app.p: The following are available online at http://www.mdpi.com/1999-4915/10/12/728/s1, Table S1. List of ZIKV Genbank accession numbers of sequences used in phylogenetic analysis, Table S2. Phylogenetic analysis of ZIKV isolates, Figure S2. ZIKV isolates differentially induce apoptosis, Figure S3. ZIKV isolates differ in infectivity at low MOI, File S1. Amino acid sequence alignment of the ZIKV isolates used in this study.
